# Toleo Website

This is a Next.js App Router single-page website with separate legal pages.

## Architecture

- Keep `app/page.tsx` as a composition layer only.
- Put large homepage sections in `components/sections/*`.
- Put shared site chrome in `components/site/*`.
- Put animation helpers in `components/motion/*`.
- Put editable business content in `lib/site-content.ts`.
- Keep Resend and secrets server-side in `app/api/contact/route.ts`.

## Design

The UI is based on the logo:

- Ink: `#181716`
- Blue: `#3060a8`
- Red: `#e00810`
- Paper: `#fffdfa`

Prefer white space, fine lines, logo-derived dots/orbits/signature strokes, and restrained
professional motion. Do not introduce a new palette unless it is intentionally derived from
the logo.

## Legal and privacy

- Legal pages live at `/impressum` and `/datenschutz`.
- Do not add tracking, analytics, marketing pixels, or non-essential cookies without updating
  the privacy page and adding consent handling.
- Never put `RESEND_API_KEY` or other secrets in client components.
